about.me: Professionally managed stake pool with the mission for cleaner energy and water. Profits from the stakes go into our solar power research and recycling.
about.company: Hidden Water is a clean energy and water company dedicated to helping the environment. We package our water in sustainable aluminum cans that are 100% recyclable and we have distribution partners like Busch Wildlife Sanctuary. We are also researching solar powered distribution models.
